<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_ardygæj" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ardygæj</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ardigæj</orth><form type="variant"><orth>ardægæj</orth></form></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>отсюда</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>from here</q></cit></sense><re><form type="lemma"><orth>ardygæj fæstæmæ</orth></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>отныне</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>from now on</q></cit></sense></re><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_ardygæj." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>fesæf ardygæj!</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>убирайся отсюда!</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>get out of here!</q></cit></cit><cit type="example"><quote>ardygæj fæstæmæ, zaǧta, næ tyxgænæg basomy kænʒæn myggagmæ tælætyl</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>отныне, сказал он, наш насильник заречется навсегда (думать о) добыче</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>from now on, he said, our rapist will forever renounce (to think about) the prey</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>135</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>fesæf ardygæj!</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>убирайся отсюда!</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>get out of here!</q></cit></cit><cit type="example"><quote>ardygæj fæstæmæ, zaǧta, næ tyxgænæg basomy kænʒæn myggagmæ tælætyl</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>отныне, сказал он, наш насильник заречется навсегда (думать о) добыче</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>from now on, he said, our rapist will forever renounce (to think about) the prey</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>135</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Буквально ‘с этой стороны’. Из <xr><ref target="#entry_a"/></xr> ‘этот’ + <xr><ref target="#entry_ardæg(i)"/></xr> ‘сторона’ в отложительном падеже, с ослаблением среднего гласного (%iæ%i → %iу%i | %ii%i). См. <xr><ref target="#entry_a"/></xr> и <xr><ref target="#entry_ærdæg"/></xr>; ср. <xr><ref target="#entry_ūrdygæj"/><ref target="#entry_ardæm"/><ref target="#entry_ardæg(i)"/></xr>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Literally ‘from this side’. From <xr><ref target="#entry_a"/></xr> ‘this’ + <xr><ref target="#entry_ærdæg"/></xr> ‘side’ in ablative case, with the weakening of the middle vowel (%iæ%i → %iу%i | %ii%i). See <xr><ref target="#entry_a"/></xr> and <xr><ref target="#entry_ærdæg"/></xr>; cf. <xr><ref target="#entry_ūrdygæj"/><ref target="#entry_ardæm"/><ref target="#entry_ardæg(i)"/></xr>.</etym></entry>